0</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nSecond century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/101_AC\" title=\"101 AC\">101</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/103_AC\" title=\"103 AC\">103</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/104_AC\" title=\"104 AC\">104</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/105_AC\" title=\"105 AC\">105</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/106_AC\" title=\"106 AC\">106</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/111_AC\" title=\"111 AC\">111</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/120_AC\" title=\"120 AC\">120</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/127_AC\" title=\"127 AC\">127</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/128_AC\" title=\"128 AC\">128</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/129_AC\" title=\"129 AC\">129</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/131_AC\" title=\"131 AC\">131</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/132_AC\" title=\"132 AC\">132</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/134_AC\" title=\"134 AC\">134</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/136_AC\" title=\"136 AC\">136</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/160_AC\" title=\"160 AC\">160</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/161_AC\" title=\"161 AC\">161</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/184_AC\" title=\"184 AC\">184</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n</div><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks collapsible uncollapsed navbox-subgroup\" style=\"border-spacing:0;width:100%;;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"float:left;width:6em;\">&#160;</span><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\nThird century since Aegon's Conquest</div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/209_AC\" title=\"209 AC\">209</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/236_AC\" title=\"236 AC\">236</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/259_AC\" title=\"259 AC\">259</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/260_AC\" title=\"260 AC\">260</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/261_AC\" title=\"261 AC\">261</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/262_AC\" title=\"262 AC\">262</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/280_AC\" title=\"280 AC\">280</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/282_AC\" title=\"282 AC\">282</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/289_AC\" title=\"289 AC\">289</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/290_AC\" title=\"290 AC\">290</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/295_AC\" title=\"295 AC\">295</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/297_AC\" title=\"297 AC\">297</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n<b>Year 10 After the Conquest</b> (<b>10 AC</b>) is a year in the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">Westerosi calendar</a>, the 10th after <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon</a>'s crowning in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> that maesters and educated people use as a reference to date the years.\n</p><p>In 10 AC the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">Dornish War</a> took a darker turn when <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenys_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenys Targaryen\">Rhaenys Targaryen</a> and her dragon <a href=\"/index.php/Meraxes\" title=\"Meraxes\">Meraxes</a> were shot down by a scorpion at <a href=\"/index.php/Hellholt\" title=\"Hellholt\">Hellholt</a>. This would begin a period of indiscriminate revenges, and the war escalated to a series of castle burnings and targeted murders of nobles known as <i>The Dragon's Wroth</i>. After a failed attempt on the life of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya</a> convinced him to establish a body of seven sworn bodyguards that would be named the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:212px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Death_of_Meraxes.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f4/Death_of_Meraxes.jpg/210px-Death_of_Meraxes.jpg\" width=\"210\" height=\"280\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f4/Death_of_Meraxes.jpg/315px-Death_of_Meraxes.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f4/Death_of_Meraxes.jpg/420px-Death_of_Meraxes.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Death_of_Meraxes.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The death of Meraxes, by Chase Stone, featured in <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Events</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Deaths\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Deaths</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Titles_and_Positions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Titles and Positions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Events\">Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> has become a true city.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I</a> and Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a> are attacked in the streets of King’s Landing, leading to Aegon ordering Visenya to choose the members of the first Seven Sworn Brothers of the Kingsguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> is formed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>A Dornish army under Lord Fowler crosses the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince%27s_Pass\" title=\"Prince&#39;s Pass\">Prince's Pass</a>, burns a dozen villages and captures <a href=\"/index.php/Nightsong\" title=\"Nightsong\">Nightsong</a>. Lord Caron, his wife and his children are made captives.</li>\n<li>A Dornish army under Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Dayne\" title=\"Joffrey Dayne\">Joffrey Dayne</a> burns fields, farms and villages for twenty leagues around <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.</li>\n<li>Aegon attacks <a href=\"/index.php/Skyreach\" title=\"Skyreach\">Skyreach</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/Balerion\" title=\"Balerion\">Balerion</a>, and Visenya attacks <a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a>.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Deaths\">Deaths</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Deaths\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenys_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenys Targaryen\">Rhaenys Targaryen</a> supposedly dies in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf796_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf796-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Meraxes\" title=\"Meraxes\">Meraxes</a>, Rhaenys's dragon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf796_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf796-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Garmon_Hightower\" title=\"Garmon Hightower\">Garmon Hightower</a>, dies in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> defending the city against the forces of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Dayne\" title=\"Joffrey Dayne\">Joffrey Dayne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Titles_and_Positions\">Titles and Positions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Titles and Positions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> is created and its first seven knights named:\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Corlys_Velaryon_(son_of_Daemon)\" title=\"Corlys Velaryon (son of Daemon)\">Corlys Velaryon</a> is named to the Kingsguard, becoming the first <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander of the Kingsguard</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robin_Darklyn\" title=\"Robin Darklyn\">Robin Darklyn</a>, known as \"Darkrobin\", is named to the Kingsguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Richard_Roote\" title=\"Richard Roote\">Richard Roote</a> is named to the Kingsguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Goode\" title=\"Gregor Goode\">Gregor Goode</a>, brother to Griffith, is named to the Kingsguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Griffith_Goode\" title=\"Griffith Goode\">Griffith Goode</a>, brother to Gregor, is named to the Kingsguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_the_Mummer\" title=\"Humfrey the Mummer\">Humfrey</a>, \"the Mummer\", a hedge knight, is named to the Kingsguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addison_Hill\" title=\"Addison Hill\">Addison Hill</a>, the \"Bastard of Cornfield\", is named to the Kingsguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Hightower\" title=\"Addam Hightower\">Addam Hightower</a> becomes the new <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Oldtown\" title=\"Lord of Oldtown\">Lord of Oldtown</a> after his father's death.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=10_AC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf41.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\">1.10</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings&#58; Aegon I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf796-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf796_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf796_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=